# Specification Diagrams

This directory contains Mermaid diagram sources (.mmd) and generated images (.svg) for specifications.

## Usage

- Place .mmd files here for spec diagrams
- Run diagram-to-image agent to convert to SVG
- Reference in spec markdown: `![Diagram](./diagrams/name.svg)`

## Naming Convention

- {feature}-data-model.mmd - ER diagram for feature data
- {feature}-user-flow.mmd - User journey diagram
- {feature}-api-sequence.mmd - API interaction sequence
- {feature}-states.mmd - State diagram for lifecycles
